\fs32  
\par }\pard \li720\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {People: Lord, have mercy. }{\fs32 
\par }\pard \qj\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 That He may deliver His people from enemies both visible and invisible, and confirm in us oneness of mind, brotherly love, and piety, let us pray to the Lord.
}{\fs32  
\par }\pard \li720\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {People: Lord, have mercy. }{\fs32 
\par }\pard \qj\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 For this land, its authorities, and Armed Forces, let us pray to the Lord. 
