\par }\pard \qj\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 For seasonable weather, abundance of the fruits of the earth, and peaceful times, let us pray to the Lord. 
\par }\pard \li720\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {People: Lord, have mercy. }{\fs32 
\par }\pard \qj\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 For travelers by sea, land, and air; for the sick, the suffering; the imprisoned and for their salvation, let us pray to the Lord.}{\fs32  
