\par }{\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 And the deacon, bowing his head to the priest saith: 
\par }\pard\plain \s45\qj\li576\ri576\sb100\sa100\sl360\slmult1\nowidctlpar\adjustright \f1\fs36\cf15 {Remember me a sinner, holy master. 
\par }\pard\plain \s25\li360\ri360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 And the priest saith:}{\fs32  
\par }\pard\plain \s45\qj\li576\ri576\sb100\sa100\sl360\slmult1\nowidctlpar\adjustright \f1\fs36\cf15 {\b\i Priest:}{ May the Lord God remember thee in His Kingdom always, now and ever and unto ages of ages. \line \~\line }{\b\i Deacon:}{ Amen. 
