\par }\pard \li720\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {People: And with thy spirit.}{\fs32  
\par }\pard\plain \s25\li360\ri360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 The deacon, having received a blessing from the priest, goeth forth and standing in the usual place, saith:
