\par }{\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 An angel of peace, a faithful guide, a guardian of our souls and bodies, let us ask of the Lord. \tab }{People: Grant this, O Lord}{\fs32  
\par }{\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 Pardon and remission of our sins and offenses, let us ask of the Lord. \tab \tab \tab \tab \tab \tab }{People: Grant this, O Lord}{\fs32  
\par }{\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 Things good and profitable for our souls and peace for the world, let us ask of the Lord. \tab \tab }{People: Grant this, O Lord.}{\fs32  
\par }{\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 \sect }\sectd \linex0\sectdefaultcl \pard\plain \qj\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 
That we may complete the remaining time of our life in peace and repentance, let us ask of the Lord.}{\fs32  
\par }\pard \li720\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {People: Grant this, O Lord.}{\fs32  
\par }\pard \qj\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 A Christian ending to our life, painless, blameless, peaceful; and a good defense before the dread Judgment Seat of Christ, let us ask of the Lord. \tab \tab 
}{People: Grant this, O Lord.}{\fs32  
\par }{\cs43\b\i\f1\fs28 Deacon:}{\fs32  }{\cs47\b\fs36 Having asked for the unity of the Faith, and the communion of the Holy Spirit, let us commit ourselves and one another, and all our life unto Christ our God. 
\par }\pard \li720\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {People: To thee, O Lord.}{\fs32  
\par }\pard\plain \s25\li360\ri360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 The priest prayeth: 
