\par }\pard\plain \s45\qj\li576\ri576\sb100\sa100\sl360\slmult1\nowidctlpar\adjustright \f1\fs36\cf15 {\cs43\b\i\fs28 Priest:}{ O God, cleanse me a sinner, and have mercy upon me. }{\cs44\i\fs30\cf6 Thrice.}{\fs30  }{
\par }\pard\plain \s25\li360\ri360\sb100\sa100\nowidctlpar\adjustright {\cs44\i\f1\fs28\cf6 And when the deacon seeth the priest stretch out his hands and touch the Holy Bread in order to make the holy elevation, he exclaimeth: 
